Package snapshot

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnalisiSnapshot
    it contains the main of the tool
    ConfigParser
    this class permits to extract the CDE host composition from the config.xml file
    Cve
    information about the single CVE-ID read in the Qualys report for each element
    Data
    object which stores info about analysis's date
    ExposedElement
    the structure stores info about the exposed elements read in the config.xml file
    Host
    represents a single host analyzed in a snapshot it stores some information about the host such as OS, hostname, etc..
    Option
    this class stores info about the configuration during a single analysis
    ReadReport
    extract data from body.txt and header.txt in order to fill objects
    Snapshot
    the root object representing a single snapshot
    StatoAttuale
    each parameter of this object represent the current visualization state this is done for report writing functions
    Vulnerability
    hybrid object which represent a vuln, practice, service, info depending on the type attribute
